# packages/phonetics-core/.gitignore
#
# Strategy for dist/ management:
#   - The root .gitignore ignores dist/ globally.
#   - Here we UN-ignore dist/ and dist/phonetic_atlas.bin because the
#     binary is a committed asset (pre-generated from panphon source).
#   - All other dist/ subdirs (generated code per language) remain ignored.
#
# See architecture.md §5: "compiled to a single static .bin asset
# checked into the repository"
#
!dist/
!dist/phonetic_atlas.bin
dist/ts/
dist/python/
dist/rust/
dist/cpp/
# Note: C is not supported by flatc v25; use C++ header with extern "C" wrappers
